<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Statlyzer - Legal</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            background-color: #121212; /* Dark mode ca în aplicația ta */
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        h1 { color: #ffffff; font-weight: 800; border-bottom: 2px solid #ff0000; padding-bottom: 10px; }
        h2 { color: #ffffff; margin-top: 30px; font-weight: 600; }
        .legal-box { background: #1e1e1e; padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #333; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .company-name { color: #ff0000; font-weight: bold; }
        hr { border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #333; margin: 40px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>LEGAL DOCUMENTS</h1>
    <p>Last updated: April 2026</p>

    <div class="legal-box">
        <h2>Terms and Conditions</h2>
        <p>Welcome to the application developed by <span class="company-name">STATLYZER SH STUDIO SRL</span>...</p>
        </div>

    <hr>

    <div class="legal-box">
        <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>This policy explains how <span class="company-name">STATLYZER SH STUDIO SRL</span> handles your data...</p>
        </div>

</body>
</html>
